extends layout

block content
  div.container
    h1 Welcome to CloudCV demonstration
  
    img(src="http://computer-vision-talks.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/logo-1.png") Logo
    p This website demonstrate interopability between Node.js and OpenCV library. It's hosted in the cloud environment. 
      | Here you will see that it's really simple to perform CPU-intense image processing routines in the cloud. 
      | A Node.js server handle client requests and calls C++ back-end. In this showcase demonstration you can try the following examples:
    
    h2 Examples
    div.row
      div.col-sm-6.col-md-3
        div.thumbnail
          img(src="/images/mandril-300x200.png",alt="...")
          div.caption
            h3 Image analysis
            p A simple image analysis that extracts key characteristics of the input image.
              | In this example the input image is analyzed and image histogram is built. 
            p
              a.btn.btn-primary(href="/demo/analysis") Try example

      div.col-sm-6.col-md-3
        div.thumbnail
          img(src="/images/lena-300x200.png",alt="...")
          div.caption
            h3 Face Recognition
            p Demonstration of face detection 
            p
              a.disabled.btn.btn-primary(href="/demo/recognition") Coming soon



      div.col-sm-6.col-md-3
        div.thumbnail
          img(src="/images/sudoku-300x200.png",alt="...")
          div.caption
            h3 Sudoku solver
            p An online sudoku solver. This sample analyze the input image and recognize the sudoku puzzle.
            p
              a.disabled.btn.btn-primary(href="/demo/sudoku") Coming soon

      div.col-sm-6.col-md-3
        div.thumbnail
          img(src="holder.js/300x200",alt="...")
          div.caption
            h3 Demo of your choice
            p Tweet me, which example you'd like to see here. 
              